  "prompt": "What is a suitable solar panel installation provider in San Jose, California CA?",
  "response": "There are several reputable solar panel installation providers in San Jose, California. Here are a few you might consider:\n\n1. **SunPower by Quality Home Services** - Known for high-efficiency solar panels and excellent customer service.\n\n2. **Bay Area Solar Solutions** - Offers a range of solar products and services, including installation and maintenance.\n\n3. **SolarCity (now part of Tesla)** - A well-known provider with a strong presence in the solar market, offering solar panels, battery storage, and financing options.\n\n4. **Sungevity** - Provides personalized solar solutions and has a user-friendly online quoting system.\n\n5. **Semper Solaris** - A veteran-owned company that focuses on high-quality installations and customer service.\n\n6. **Nexamp** - Offers both residential and commercial solar solutions, with a focus on community solar projects.\n\nWhen choosing a provider, consider factors such as customer reviews, warranties, financing options, and the company's experience in the industry. It's also a good idea to get multiple quotes and compare them before making a decision.",
